result.formatted_address: Shop 112B, 28 Beach Rd, Repulse Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Fratelli Artisan Pasta Bar

reviews.text: First of all, don't misunderstand that restaurants at The Pulse can see the beach. It doesn't, in case of Fratelli, see photo. You can see the pavement and some trees. As to this restaurant, it is ok if you do mind paying more for food which is very so so. I ordered a Lasagna, which didn't taste like one, a tiramisu, which has ton of sugar in it and a bottle of still water. It was HK$330 for a one person lunch. Rating show it all.

Great service and friendly staff. The food on the other hand was not up to scratch, the pappardelle was undercooked and far from Al dente. The cacio de pepe did not have enough pecorino romano to form the saltiness in the sauce. The orecchiette with nduja was surprisingly bland, it was not even close to having that sensational nduja heat. This would all be ok if the price wasn't so high.
Lovely spot by the beach. Great place to watch the sunset. Must try the veal meatballs!
Environment quite European. Pasta with clams, clams good, pasta needs some sauce.
Love the pastas and the friendly service here

reviews.text: It was a great place! Good location next to repulse bay with restaurants of different cuisines. I enjoyed the beer festival very much, good spots for photo taking and the food and and beer were stunning! Perfect for weekend activities.
Nice location in the rooftop. Good unique beers to try out, great view with the bay and very special ladder for photos. Wish it's bigger and more stalls.

Went to the Pirate's Beer Fest today and had a total blast.  There's a great selection of food and beer available, staff are uber friendly and helpful.  The game stalls were fun as well, won myself a frog and banana plushie.  There are cabanas on one side of the venue and great photo taking spots. Overall was a good day out!
Nice place. Terrace on the beach with premium beers. Highly recommendable
Nice beach with many amenities and a grocery store all within an area.
